  "description": "Two Wavefolder voices at different fold depths — Voice 1 at 2.3 folds (Buchla gentleness), Voice 2 at 6.8 folds (Serge aggression). HAMMER at -0.2 introduces light ring modulation between the two folded spectra, creating sum-and-difference tones between their harmonic series. Triangle modulation on both fold depths via LFOs at coprime rates (0.7 Hz and 1.1 Hz) creates a pattern that never repeats.",
